
Till Basket Fields

1.	acctCash	- retail value of products payable by cash only.
2.	acctCredit	- retail value of products payable by either cash or card.
3.	acctNews	- amount taken to pay a news account. This is the only item for which 
				  cheques can be accepted.
4.	prize		- total of prizes rung in.
5.	discount	- total discount allowed.
6.	balance		- current amount owed by customer excluding prizes & discounts.
